htmlDescription.htmlText:
This is a comfortable , bright bedroom, with the bathroom in the hallway. The bathroom is only shared with me, the host. The home is located 3 blocks from the beach and walking distance to the Redondo Beach Pier.
This space is a prime location , 7 miles from the LAX Airport, 2 miles from the Del Amo Shopping Center, and with quick access to Hermosa and Manhattan Beach.
Guest will find restaurants within walking distance as well as a short drive to Whole Foods, CVS and Starbucks.

The space
This bedroom is at the end of the hallway on the second floor. The shared bathroom is a full bath, with a sink, tub and shower; and it is only shared with me the host.
An additional 1/2 bath (sink and toilet)
Is located on the first floor.
The room has a queen bed and soft sheets.
Currently, there are two bedrooms dedicated for Airbnb guests. The other bedroom is the master suite, and has its own private bathroom inside the bedroom.
Please note that in keeping with social distancing guidelines, only the guests booking the room are allowed in the house.

Guest access
Guests have access to this room, the dining room, and the patio.
Only the guests that have booked will be allowed in the house.
You are welcome to use the kitchen refrigerator to store your perishables.
There is interaction in the kitchen and patio with other guests or myself.

During your stay
I enjoy hosting and meeting new people. I am available to answer any questions; and can be easily reached by cell phone or text.

Other things to note
Guests will have access to the bedroom and the dinning room.
Currently I disinfect the common areas with alcohol. I also use an Air Purifier with a Hepa filter and UVC sanitizer to disinfect the bedrooms.
I provide parking in the driveway, in front of the house. This is very convenient, so you don’t have to be looking for street parking.
Very easy check-in via a keypad.
Please let me know If you need an earlier check in.
Lastly, the washer and dryer are not accessible to guests. There are public laundromats nearby.

section.subtitle: AirCover is comprehensive protection included for free with every booking.

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: 24-hour Safety Line
features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.
